  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RegistroPontoService, com.liferay.portal.kernel.module.framework.service.IdentifiableOSGiService, com.liferay.portal.kernel.service.BaseService

    public class RegistroPontoServiceImpl
extends RegistroPontoServiceBaseImpl
    The implementation of the registro ponto remote service.

    All custom service methods should be put in this class. Whenever methods are added, rerun ServiceBuilder to copy their definitions into the RegistroPontoService interface.

    This is a remote service. Methods of this service are expected to have security checks based on the propagated JAAS credentials because this service can be accessed remotely.

    Author:
    Peterson Morais
    See Also:
    RegistroPontoServiceBaseImpl, RegistroPontoServiceUtil
